      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>&gt; @Compendium[sfrpg.rules.nwRAcqBuoleMkfZE]{Weapon Accessories}</p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListWeaponAccessories_ctl00_LabelName\">Weapons can be fitted with special grips that provide various advantages. You can combine grips by paying the combined price of the grips, but only if all grips are integrated into a weapon. Their benefits stack. The benefits of a grip depend on its type.</span></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListWeaponAccessories_ctl00_LabelName\">Only small arms can have a folding grip, and it must be integrated with the weapon. As a move action, you can fold or unfold a folding grip, granting you a +2 circumstance bonus to Sleight of Hand checks to hide the small arm on your person.&nbsp;</span></p>"
